        <member name="T:FiftyOne.IpIntelligence.CountriesAll.Data.IIpCountriesAllData">
            <summary>
            Data interface for the IpCountriesAll engine output.
            Contains flat (non-weighted) lists of all country codes,
            ordered by weight descending for matched codes followed by
            remaining codes alphabetically.
            </summary>
        </member>
        <member name="P:FiftyOne.IpIntelligence.CountriesAll.Data.IIpCountriesAllData.CountryCodesGeographicalAll">
